       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI77206.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI77206.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Anulaçăo de Factura                                        *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI77206         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5012 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6404 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV7720.
       COPY COCV7721.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0010.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT5012 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT5012'.
           05 CON-COVT6404 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT6404'.
           05 CON-NC       PIC X(02) VALUE 'NC'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-TOT-PAG         PIC S9(15)V9(2) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.
           05 WS-NTOTPAG-ACT     PIC S9(15)V9(2) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.
           05 WS-NTAXPAG-ACT     PIC S9(15)V9(2) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.
           05 WS-NSEQ            PIC S9(10)      COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.
           05 WS-NVALLIQ         PIC S9(15)V9(2) COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI77206'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI77206         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.

            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV7720-MSG.
           MOVE COCV7720-ASE               TO COCV7721-ASE.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV7720-ADE               TO COCV7721-ADE.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-VALIDACOES
                 THRU 2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-PROCESSA
                 THRU 2200-PROCESSA-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDACOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7720-REFNCR EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO   TO COCV7721-REFNCR-S
               MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT   TO COCV7721-REFNCR-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC          TO COCV7721-REFNCR-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF COCV7720-REFNCR(1:3) NOT NUMERIC  OR
                 COCV7720-REFNCR(4:1) NOT = '/'    OR
                 COCV7720-REFNCR(5:4) NOT NUMERIC  OR
                 COCV7720-REFNCR(9:2) NOT = SPACES
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7721-REFNCR-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-MASK-NC-INV   TO COCV7721-REFNCR-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV7721-REFNCR-CAPLIC
              END-IF

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7720-DDATEMINCR EQUAL SPACES
             OR COCV7720-DDATEMINCR EQUAL COCK0002-DATA-MIN
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7721-DDATEMINCR-S
               MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV7721-DDATEMINCR-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV7721-DDATEMINCR-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7720-CMOTANU EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO   TO COCV7721-CMOTANU-S
               MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT   TO COCV7721-CMOTANU-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC          TO COCV7721-CMOTANU-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV7720-CTIPANU EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO   TO COCV7721-CTIPANU-S
               MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT   TO COCV7721-CTIPANU-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC          TO COCV7721-CTIPANU-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

      *--- Para já, só pode ser Total e năo Parcial
      *    IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *      IF COCV7720-CTIPANU EQUAL COCK0002-CTIPANU-PARC
      *        MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
      *        MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO   TO COCV7721-CTIPANU-S
      *        MOVE COCK0001-FUNC-NDISP      TO COCV7721-CTIPANU-MSG
      *        MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC          TO COCV7721-CTIPANU-CAPLIC
      *      END-IF
      *    END-IF.

      *--- Ler a factura para obter dados antes de actualizar
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2170-LER-COT50  THRU 2170-LER-COT50-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- Valida se existe a Referencia da NC repetida
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2150-VER-REPETE THRU 2150-VER-REPETE-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2170-LER-COT50
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2170-LER-COT50.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2170-LER-COT50     ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV7720-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCD5012-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE COCV7720-NIDINVOICE    TO COCD5012-NIDINVOICE.
           MOVE COCV7720-REFINVOICE    TO COCD5012-GREFINV.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT
                       GCLIENTE
                     , DDATAINSER
                     , DDATAEMISS
                     , DDATAEMIS2
                     , DDATEDUE
                     , CPRAZO
                     , NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , NTAXAMOUNT
                     , GDESCINVOICE
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST
                     , CTIPDOC
                     , CMOEDA
                     , CIMPOSTO
                     , NOTAS
                     , NTOTPAG
                     , NTAXPAG
                     , NTOTRET
                     , NTAXRET
                     , NTOTNCR
                     , NTAXNCR
                     , CEMPRESA
                 INTO
                       :COCD5012-GCLIENTE
                     , :COCD5012-DDATAINSER
                     , :COCD5012-DDATAEMISS
                     , :COCD5012-DDATAEMIS2
                     , :COCD5012-DDATEDUE
                     , :COCD5012-CPRAZO
                     , :COCD5012-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , :COCD5012-NTAXAMOUNT
                     , :COCD5012-GDESCINVOICE
                     , :COCD5012-CUSERID
                     , :COCD5012-HTIMEST
                     , :COCD5012-CTIPDOC
                     , :COCD5012-CMOEDA
                     , :COCD5012-CIMPOSTO
                     , :COCD5012-NOTAS
                     , :COCD5012-NTOTPAG
                     , :COCD5012-NTAXPAG
                     , :COCD5012-NTOTRET
                     , :COCD5012-NTAXRET
                     , :COCD5012-NTOTNCR
                     , :COCD5012-NTAXNCR
                     , :COCD5012-CEMPRESA
                  FROM  COVT5012_INVOICES
                 WHERE GREFINV      = :COCD5012-GREFINV
                   AND NIDPROJECTO  = :COCD5012-NIDPROJECTO
                   AND NIDINVOICE   = :COCD5012-NIDINVOICE
                   FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5012 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF DB2-OK
                MOVE COCD5012-NTOTPAG TO WS-NTOTPAG-ACT
                MOVE COCD5012-NTAXPAG TO WS-NTAXPAG-ACT
             ELSE
                MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7721-REFNCR-S
                MOVE COCK0001-REFINVOICE-N-EXISTS
                                            TO COCV7721-REFNCR-MSG
                MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV7721-REFNCR-CAPLIC
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2170-LER-COT50-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2150-VER-REPETE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2150-VER-REPETE.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2150-VER-REPETE    ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV7720-REFNCR       TO COCD5012-GREFNCR.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT
                       GREFNCR
                 INTO
                       :COCD5012-GREFNCR
                  FROM  COVT5012_INVOICES
                 WHERE  GREFNCR     = :COCD5012-GREFNCR
                   AND  CEMPRESA    = :COCD5012-CEMPRESA
                 FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5012  TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV7721-REFNCR-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-REFNCR-REPETE TO COCV7721-REFNCR-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV7721-REFNCR-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2150-VER-REPETE-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-PROCESSA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-PROCESSA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-PROCESSA      ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV7720-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCD5012-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE COCV7720-NIDINVOICE    TO COCD5012-NIDINVOICE.
           MOVE COCV7720-REFINVOICE    TO COCD5012-GREFINV.
           MOVE COCV7720-REFNCR        TO COCD5012-GREFNCR.
           MOVE COCV7720-DDATEMINCR    TO COCD5012-DDATEMINCR.
           MOVE COCV7720-CMOTANU       TO COCD5012-CMOTANU.
           MOVE COCV7720-CTIPANU       TO COCD5012-CTIPANU.

           IF COCV7720-CTIPANU = COCK0002-CTIPANU-TOT
              MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-ANUL  TO COCD5012-CSTATUS
           ELSE
              MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-PPAG  TO COCD5012-CSTATUS
           END-IF.

      *    MOVE ZEROS                  TO COCD5012-NTOTPAG.
      *    MOVE ZEROS                  TO COCD5012-NTAXPAG.
           ADD  COCD5012-NTOTNCR       TO COCD5012-NTOTPAG.
           ADD  COCD5012-NTAXNCR       TO COCD5012-NTAXPAG.

           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I    TO COCD5012-CUSERID.

           EXEC SQL
                UPDATE COVT5012_INVOICES
                SET    CSTATUS      = :COCD5012-CSTATUS
                     , GREFNCR      = :COCD5012-GREFNCR
                     , DDATEMINCR   = :COCD5012-DDATEMINCR
                     , CMOTANU      = :COCD5012-CMOTANU
                     , CTIPANU      = :COCD5012-CTIPANU
                     , NTOTPAG      = :COCD5012-NTOTPAG
                     , NTAXPAG      = :COCD5012-NTAXPAG
                     , CUSERID      = :COCD5012-CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST      =  CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                 WHERE GREFINV      = :COCD5012-GREFINV
                   AND NIDPROJECTO  = :COCD5012-NIDPROJECTO
                   AND NIDINVOICE   = :COCD5012-NIDINVOICE
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5012               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF DB2-OK
               MOVE COCD5012-CSTATUS    TO COCV7721-CSTATUS
               MOVE COCD5012-GREFNCR    TO COCV7721-REFNCR
               MOVE COCD5012-DDATEMINCR TO COCV7721-NVALREC
               MOVE COCD5012-CMOTANU    TO COCV7721-CMOTANU
               MOVE COCD5012-CTIPANU    TO COCV7721-CTIPANU
             ELSE
               IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                          TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-REFINVOICE-N-EXISTS
                                          TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE-CAPLIC
               ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2   TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2500-INSERE-COT64
                 THRU 2500-INSERE-COT64-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2200-PROCESSA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2500-INSERE-COT64
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2500-INSERE-COT64.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2500-INSERE-COT64       '    TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2600-PREENCHE-COT64
              THRU 2600-PREENCHE-COT64-EXIT.

           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I TO COCD6404-CUSERID.

           EXEC SQL
                INSERT INTO COVT6404_INVPAY
                (
                   NIDINVOICE
                 , NSEQ
                 , NIDPROJECTO
                 , GCLIENTE
                 , DDATAINSER
                 , DDATAEMISS
                 , DDATAEMIS2
                 , DDATEDUE
                 , CPRAZO
                 , NTOTALAMOUNT
                 , NTAXAMOUNT
                 , GDESCINVOICE
                 , CSTATUS
                 , CUSERID
                 , HTIMEST
                 , GREFINV
                 , DPAG
                 , CTIPDOC
                 , CMOEDA
                 , CIMPOSTO
                 , NOTAS
                 , CTIPFAC
                 , NTOTPAG
                 , NTAXPAG
                 , NTOTRET
                 , NTAXRET
                 , GREFNCR
                 , DDATEMINCR
                )
                VALUES (
                       :COCD6404-NIDINVOICE
                     , :COCD6404-NSEQ
                     , :COCD6404-NIDPROJECTO
                     , :COCD6404-GCLIENTE
                     , :COCD6404-DDATAINSER
                     , :COCD6404-DDATAEMISS
                     , :COCD6404-DDATAEMIS2
                     , :COCD6404-DDATEDUE
                     , :COCD6404-CPRAZO
                     , :COCD6404-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , :COCD6404-NTAXAMOUNT
                     , :COCD6404-GDESCINVOICE
                     , :COCD6404-CSTATUS
                     , :COCD6404-CUSERID
                     ,  CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                     , :COCD6404-GREFINV
                     , :COCD6404-DPAG
                     , :COCD6404-CTIPDOC
                     , :COCD6404-CMOEDA
                     , :COCD6404-CIMPOSTO
                     , :COCD6404-NOTAS
                     , :COCD6404-CTIPFAC
                     , :COCD6404-NTOTPAG
                     , :COCD6404-NTAXPAG
                     , :COCD6404-NTOTRET
                     , :COCD6404-NTAXRET
                     , :COCD6404-GREFNCR
                     , :COCD6404-DDATEMINCR
                )
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT6404               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF NOT DB2-OK
               MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2 TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2  TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2500-INSERE-COT64-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2600-PREENCHE-COT64
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2600-PREENCHE-COT64.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2600-PREENCHE-COT64' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV7720-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCD5012-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE COCV7720-NIDINVOICE    TO COCD5012-NIDINVOICE.
           MOVE COCV7720-REFINVOICE    TO COCD5012-GREFINV.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT
                       GCLIENTE
                     , DDATAINSER
                     , DDATAEMISS
                     , DDATAEMIS2
                     , DDATEDUE
                     , CPRAZO
                     , NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , NTAXAMOUNT
                     , GDESCINVOICE
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST
                     , CTIPDOC
                     , CMOEDA
                     , CIMPOSTO
                     , NOTAS
                     , NTOTPAG
                     , NTAXPAG
                     , NTOTRET
                     , NTAXRET
                     , CTIPFAC
                     , GREFNCR
                     , DDATEMINCR
                     , NTOTNCR
                     , NTAXNCR
                 INTO
                       :COCD5012-GCLIENTE
                     , :COCD5012-DDATAINSER
                     , :COCD5012-DDATAEMISS
                     , :COCD5012-DDATAEMIS2
                     , :COCD5012-DDATEDUE
                     , :COCD5012-CPRAZO
                     , :COCD5012-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , :COCD5012-NTAXAMOUNT
                     , :COCD5012-GDESCINVOICE
                     , :COCD5012-CUSERID
                     , :COCD5012-HTIMEST
                     , :COCD5012-CTIPDOC
                     , :COCD5012-CMOEDA
                     , :COCD5012-CIMPOSTO
                     , :COCD5012-NOTAS
                     , :COCD5012-NTOTPAG
                     , :COCD5012-NTAXPAG
                     , :COCD5012-NTOTRET
                     , :COCD5012-NTAXRET
                     , :COCD5012-CTIPFAC
                     , :COCD5012-GREFNCR
                     , :COCD5012-DDATEMINCR
                     , :COCD5012-NTOTNCR
                     , :COCD5012-NTAXNCR
                  FROM  COVT5012_INVOICES
                 WHERE GREFINV      = :COCD5012-GREFINV
                   AND NIDPROJECTO  = :COCD5012-NIDPROJECTO
                   AND NIDINVOICE   = :COCD5012-NIDINVOICE
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5012 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF DB2-OK
               MOVE COCD5012-GREFINV         TO COCD6404-GREFINV
               MOVE COCD5012-NIDPROJECTO     TO COCD6404-NIDPROJECTO
               MOVE COCD5012-NIDINVOICE      TO COCD6404-NIDINVOICE
               PERFORM 2700-OBTEM-SEQ
                  THRU 2700-OBTEM-SEQ-EXIT
               MOVE WS-NSEQ                  TO COCD6404-NSEQ
               MOVE COCD5012-GCLIENTE        TO COCD6404-GCLIENTE
               MOVE COCD5012-DDATAINSER      TO COCD6404-DDATAINSER
               MOVE COCD5012-DDATAEMISS      TO COCD6404-DDATAEMISS
               MOVE COCD5012-DDATAEMIS2      TO COCD6404-DDATAEMIS2
               MOVE COCD5012-DDATEDUE        TO COCD6404-DDATEDUE
               MOVE COCD5012-CPRAZO          TO COCD6404-CPRAZO
      *        MOVE COCD5012-NTOTALAMOUNT    TO COCD6404-NTOTALAMOUNT
      *        MOVE COCD5012-NTAXAMOUNT      TO COCD6404-NTAXAMOUNT
               MOVE COCD5012-NTOTNCR         TO COCD6404-NTOTALAMOUNT
               MOVE COCD5012-NTAXNCR         TO COCD6404-NTAXAMOUNT
               MOVE COCD5012-GREFNCR         TO COCD6404-GREFNCR
               MOVE COCD5012-DDATEMINCR      TO COCD6404-DDATEMINCR
               MOVE COCD5012-NTOTRET         TO COCD6404-NTOTRET
               MOVE COCD5012-NTAXRET         TO COCD6404-NTAXRET
               MOVE COCD5012-GDESCINVOICE    TO COCD6404-GDESCINVOICE
               MOVE COCD5012-CSTATUS         TO COCD6404-CSTATUS
               MOVE COCV7720-DDATEMINCR      TO COCD6404-DPAG
               MOVE CON-NC                   TO COCD6404-CTIPDOC
               MOVE COCD5012-CMOEDA          TO COCD6404-CMOEDA
               MOVE COCD5012-CIMPOSTO        TO COCD6404-CIMPOSTO
               MOVE COCD5012-NOTAS           TO COCD6404-NOTAS
               COMPUTE COCD6404-NTOTPAG =  WS-NTOTPAG-ACT * ( -1 )
               COMPUTE COCD6404-NTAXPAG =  WS-NTAXPAG-ACT * ( -1 )
               MOVE COCD5012-CTIPFAC         TO COCD6404-CTIPFAC
             ELSE
               IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                          TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-REFINVOICE-N-EXISTS
                                          TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC     TO COCV7721-REFINVOICE-CAPLIC
               ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2   TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2600-PREENCHE-COT64-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2700-OBTEM-SEQ
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2700-OBTEM-SEQ.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2700-OBTEM-SEQ         '    TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
              SELECT COUNT(NSEQ)
                INTO :WS-NSEQ
                FROM COVT6404_INVPAY
               WHERE NIDINVOICE  = :COCD6404-NIDINVOICE
                 AND NIDPROJECTO = :COCD6404-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6404               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF DB2-OK
               ADD 1 TO WS-NSEQ
             ELSE
               IF DB2-NOTFND
                 CONTINUE
               ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2   TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

       2700-OBTEM-SEQ-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV7721-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV7721-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV7721-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *==============================================================
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0010.
           COPY VIAP0016.
